wsd.ass

Class Log

  • java.lang.Object
    • wsd.ass.Log
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Log
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Log class is a Bean/POJO which defines a vehicle log entry within the system. It contains a sub-class Hidden which represents the attribute 'hidden' and its own elements.
    Author:
    Calvin
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
